        </ul>

        <h2 id="local-keyword-research">Step 5-6: Local Keyword Research and Implementation</h2>

        <h3>Step 5: Target High-Intent Local Keywords</h3>
        <p>Focus on keywords that drive immediate service calls. These convert at 3.2x higher rates than generic HVAC terms:</p>

