          <li><strong>Emergency keywords:</strong> "emergency HVAC repair [city]," "24 hour AC repair near me"</li>
          <li><strong>Service-specific:</strong> "furnace installation [city]," "ductwork repair [zip code]"</li>
          <li><strong>Seasonal:</strong> "AC tune up [city]" (spring), "furnace maintenance [city]" (fall)</li>
          <li><strong>Problem-focused:</strong> "HVAC not working [city]," "no heat [city]"</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Step 6: Optimize Website for Local Keywords</h3>
        <p>Your website needs location-specific pages for each major service area. Companies with dedicated location pages rank 67% higher for "near me" searches:</p>

