          <li>Create service area pages for each major city (minimum 500 words)</li>
          <li>Include NAP information on every page</li>
          <li>Add local schema markup to all location pages</li>
          <li>Optimize title tags: "HVAC Repair [City] | 24/7 Emergency Service | [Business Name]"</li>
        </ul>

